data.description: Welcome to Fara Estates! This single-story condo is located in a well-maintained gated community on the east side of Modesto! Offering 2 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and 912 sqft of living space. The HOA covers the water, sewer, garbage, security, exterior maintenance on grounds, building exterior with roof included, and insurance on structure. Nice open concept with tile in the main area and carpet in the rooms, your own private fenced patio, and a finished two car garage! FHA financing available! Make this your home for the New Year!
